      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
