    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have softened, stir through the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> toasted sesame seeds </strong>– this is your <strong>hoisin meat-free mince & mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
