    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>to the side of a bowl and top with the<strong> cooked brown rice </strong>and <strong>hoisin meat-free mince & mushrooms</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Tip: Make loaded lettuce cups by adding filling to the<strong> </strong>lettuce leaves!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
